window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>When the divide between the fae world and the human world is torn apart, Aleric Bayne is thrown into the ensuing chaos. Hurt and disoriented, the werewolf finds himself in a hospital emergency room.</p> <p>When other fae creatures begin to show up, Aleric sneaks them into the D wing of the hospital. With no one else able to treat their unusual conditions, Aleric steps into the role of Dr. Wolf. He has one goal in mind, to help the fae and close the Rift.</p> <p>But Dr. Wolf has walls around the memories of his own broken past that threaten to unravel the world he is holding together by a thread.</p>"; 
